[[cell]]
Target is the owner of Zhejiang EmblemNorth Co., Ltd, a large agricultural and fishery conglomerate based out of Hangzhou, Zhejiang, China, controversial for its use of Uyghur slave labor and massive illegal overfishing practices. Target is a reality bender suffering from paranoid and narcissistic personality disorder. Target has repeatedly used his abilities to manipulate other individuals for his own entertainment, and to sabotage potential competitors. Target has rendered conventional weaponry non-functional within his area of effect.
[[/cell]]
[[/row]]
[[row]]
[[hcell style="text-align:right"]]
Status:
[[/hcell]]
[[cell]]
**##green|APPROVED##**
[[/cell]]
[[/row]]
[[/table]]

SCP-9148 was successfully deployed against target. Onset of prion disease symptoms worsened target's existing psychological disorders and rendered his ontokinetic abilities highly unstable. Target was terminated by GOC [[[speed-of-hate|Strike Team 4321 ("Black Swan Hypothesis")]]] using experimental paraweaponry. The full extent of collateral damage and civilian casualties is unknown, but estimated to total almost 300 million dollars in property damage and reparations paid by the GOC to survivors. Population of whale sharks in the vicinity of the Galápagos Islands still remains in steady decline.

[[/div]]
[[/div]]

